<h2>Welcome to your DB convertor</h2>
<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6">
      <div class="field1">
        <p>Copy-paste your XML file exported from <a href="https://kitt.lewagon.com/db/">Kitt</a> and use it to generate your models.</p>
        <form action="/convert_from_xml" method="post">
          <textarea rows="15" cols="60" name="xml" placeholder="XML file to convert to rails models"></textarea>
          <br>
          <input type="submit">
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6">
      <div class="field2">
        <p>Copy-paste your schema.rb file generated by Rails to generate XML file and use it on <a href="https://kitt.lewagon.com/db/">Kitt</a> to visualize your DB.</p>
        <form action="/convert_from_schema" method="post">
          <textarea rows="15" cols="60" name="schema" placeholder="Convert rails schema to XML"></textarea>
          <br>
          <input type="submit">
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
